"{\"uid\": \"mercurynews.com-2024-07-25-speedo-olympic-swimsuit\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Today's e-Edition Get Morning Report and other email newsletters Get Morning Report and other email newsletters Today's e-Edition Trending: By JENNA FRYER, AP National Writer PARIS (AP) - It's usually not a good sign when a swimsuit needs instructions for how to put it on.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999902710771842, \"rank\": 9.728961072744165e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999902710771842, \"rank\": 9.728961072744165e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today's e-Edition Get Morning Report\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"other email newsletters\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"Get Morning Report\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 83}, {\"ngram\": \"other email newsletters\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"Today's e-Edition Trending\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"JENNA FRYER\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"AP\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"a good sign\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimsuit\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"instructions\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More concerning?\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you learn that even Olympians need about 10 minutes to get into Speedo's newFastskin LZR Intent and LZR Valorsuits.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.000978264242391e-24, \"text\": \"Speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LZR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even Olympians\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"about 10 minutes\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"LZR Valorsuits\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Determined to squeeze into the latest skin-tight polyurethane compression suit, I grabbed a red Pure Valor 2.0 openback kneeskin and entered the crowded women's changing room at The Molitor Hotel to see what the big deal is about the newest version of the suit many swimmers will be wearing during the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\", \"score\": 0.9999817977792625, \"rank\": 1.8202460123316828e-05, \"text\": \"Molitor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest skin-tight polyurethane compression suit\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"a red Pure Valor 2.0 openback kneeskin\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowded women's changing room\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"the big deal\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the newest version\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"many swimmers\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wedged inside the changing room, I followed the directions and rolled up the leg openings to work around the rubber gripper at the bottom that is designed to help the suit stick to your skin.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the changing room\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"the directions\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"the leg openings\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the rubber gripper\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"your skin\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who did not listen to the instructions were grunting, tugging and wiggling as they tried to shimmy the suit now stuck to their calves.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the instructions\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"their calves\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was ahead of them all and had the suit to my thighs!\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"my thighs\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race was on!\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then the trouble began.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trouble\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I pulled and the suit moved less than an inch.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"an inch\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I pulled some more and same result.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some more and same result\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not a chance this thing was making it over my hips.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not a chance\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"this thing\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"my hips\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Fastskin is not like a regular one-piece bathing suit.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Fastskin\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"a regular one-piece bathing suit\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looks more like a singlet worn by a wrestler and is meant to sit above the knee and worn like a one-piece romper.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a singlet\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrestler\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the knee\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-piece romper\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A very, very, tight romper.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A very, very, tight romper\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Introduced earlier this year and developed by Speedo's Aqualab research and development facility, the Fastskin is engineered from Lamoral Space Tech material that is used on satellites.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.000978264242391e-24, \"text\": \"Speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}, {\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fastskin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lamoral Space Tech material\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"satellites\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"High-level competition suits have been improving for years, and this version is more aerodynamic and repels water to help swimmers stay buoyant.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"High-level competition suits\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"this version\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"more aerodynamic and repels water\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was getting into this thing - the most expensive swimsuit I have ever worn, at about $550 - no matter what.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this thing\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now I was sweating - really sweating - as I tried every dressing room hack ever learned.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every dressing room hack\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's too tight,\\\" said one woman.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one woman\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They gave me the wrong size,\\\" grumbled another.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wrong size\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, all the suits were sized correctly.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the suits\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They just really are that difficult to put on.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I finally figured out my best approach was to take the suit inch by inch, pulling up any bunched material gained with every tug.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best approach\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit inch\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"inch\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"any bunched material\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"every tug\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I foolishly neglected to set a timer, but it's fair to say it took me more than 10 minutes to get into the suit.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a timer\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 10 minutes\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even so, I felt like a gold medalist when I finally finished the task - a full workout in itself.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medalist\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"a full workout\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drenched in sweat, I headed to the Molitor's indoor pool, which is considered one of Paris' most popular swimming baths and opened in 1929.\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\", \"score\": 0.9999817977792625, \"rank\": 1.8202460123316828e-05, \"text\": \"Molitor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Jean_Joseph_Molitor\"}, {\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7695642436213486e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager to get into the water but was stopped by Kate Wilton, Aqualab's senior director of competitive product.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999999751753452, \"rank\": 2.4824641597743566e-07, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 2765, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilton,_Wiltshire\", \"score\": 0.5579062770501768, \"rank\": 0.4386053350137195, \"text\": \"Wilton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilton,_Wiltshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilton,_Wiltshire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"Aqualab's senior director\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive product\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wanted me to note the wicking ability of the suit, and sure enough, as I splashed water on myself, it dribbled down the suit in small droplets.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wicking ability\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2864}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"small droplets\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speedo says the 2.0 version of the suit has the lowest water absorption and is the most water repellent of any of its previous products.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2971, \"end\": 2977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.000978264242391e-24, \"text\": \"Speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2.0 version\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"the lowest water absorption\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"the most water repellent\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"its previous products\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was finally time to swim.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Led by Cullen Jones, the first Black swimmer to hold a world record, we were instructed to \\\"streamline\\\" off the wall and see how far we could travel under water with our arms crossed above our heads and without kicking.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cullen Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cullen_Jones\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"our arms\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"our heads\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a solid two decades since I have done any \\\"real\\\" swimming, but in this suit, I covered some decent distance in coming up about the halfway point of the Molitor's 33-meter pool.\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a solid two decades\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"any \\\"real\\\" swimming\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"this suit\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"some decent distance\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"the halfway point\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Molitor's 33-meter pool\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next it was time to test the buoyancy, which I did by floating on my back.\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"the buoyancy\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"my back\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This suit was like a life preserver in that I could float without moving a muscle and stay nearly on top of the water.\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This suit\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"a muscle\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3726}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's one of the main benefits of the suit - the fabric zone on the rear targets drag reduction, making swimmers feel like they are on top of the water.\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 3895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main benefits\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"the fabric zone\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"the rear targets drag reduction\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3881}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt it immediately when I actually started swimming.\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not have to think about form or wonder if my torso was dipping lower in the water than my head and arms.\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 4062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"my torso\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4008}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4039}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4052}, {\"ngram\": \"arms\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt perfectly aligned as I swam several laps of freestyle.\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several laps\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4110}, {\"ngram\": \"freestyle\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 80 world records have been set since the first version of these suits were introduced at the 2000 Sydney Olympics, where 83% of medals were won by swimmers wearing it.\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.098000166962862e-20, \"text\": \"2000 Sydney Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 80 world records\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4147}, {\"ngram\": \"the first version\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4185}, {\"ngram\": \"these suits\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"83%\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4265}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Phelps won eight gold medals wearing the LZR Racer at the Beijing Olympics.\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4299, \"end\": 4313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4336994306570076e-61, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 4348, \"end\": 4357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LZR Racer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LZR_Racer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight gold medals\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4335}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Olympics\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did the suit make me any faster?\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Olympians believe it does, I can not be sure because I have not swam competitively in years, but after slowly wedging myself into it, the suit had me comfortable, floating above the water and believing I could take on Katie Ledecky.\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4641, \"end\": 4654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4565}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4674, \"end\": 4689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4668}]}]}"